sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant WAF as Web Application Firewall
    participant App as Web Application
    participant IdP as Identity Provider
    participant DB as Database

    User->>WAF: HTTPS / 443 / Access application
    WAF->>App: HTTPS / 443 / Forward request
    App->>IdP: OIDC / 443 / Authenticate user
    IdP-->>App: Token / Claims
    App->>DB: DB Protocol / Port / Read-write data
    DB-->>App: Query response
    App-->>User: Application response
